findings.title: Out of gas
findings.description: The functions setAutomatedMarketMakerPair(), getLiquidityBacking(), and manualSyncPairs() may cause an OUT_OF_GAS exception if there is a long addresses list in _markerPairs array.

findings.title: Rounding error
findings.description: At gonSwapThreshold value calculation division goes first which can cause rounding errors because Solidity does not support floating points.

findings.title: Owner privileges (In the period when the owner is not renounced)
findings.description: The contract owner has excessive privileges to modify critical parameters and perform sensitive actions.
